      "heading": "",
      "textPreview": "JFK offers Hidden Disabilities Sunflower lanyards to travelers with non-visible disabilities such as autism, PTSD, hearing loss, or chronic conditions. Wearing a lanyard is a simple way to let airport staff know you may need a little extra help, time, or understanding during your",
