      "className": "chakra-stack TitleLockup_description__77Ju9 css-sekf8j",
      "ariaLabel": "",
      "heading": "",
      "textPreview": "For our travelers who may feel overwhelmed by the busy airport setting, including neurodivergent individuals and people with sensory sensitivies, sensory spaces offer a quiet, low-stimulation environment. We're excited to offer these spaces in the near future!",
